{"tid":2060973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［齊施壓］深藍青年機構KELY 彈弓手刪除黑警販毒報導","createTime":"2020-06-12T04:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T04:57:31.000Z","uid":269052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5936ed99a317636394eefc315244ace3ab2737c1","tid":2060973,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQEUSje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQEUSje.jpg&h=04e5b899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說有間青年機構啟勵扶青會(KELY Support Group)喺instagram上傳咗販冰兵偷冰嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n班深藍高層為咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撐警</span>，一個唔該就施壓刪除咗個post<br />\n<br />\n為免哩個深藍機構繼續洗班青少年腦，大家一齊喺佢地Facebook留言出返哩個post，再send email叫佢地解釋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">深藍機構 一個都嫌多！</span>"},{"pid":"7950d8cb2eb646475ad80fb8952d4d0e3b374c29","tid":2060973,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da8948452a6856317ca62b5b7ee5798b4b10d3bf","tid":2060973,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法，<br />\n除非你係警察"},{"pid":"1d66b8cf5e6f65bdc869e651b43c2c34119aada3","tid":2060973,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da8948452a6856317ca62b5b7ee5798b4b10d3bf","tid":2060973,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T04:56:34.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法，<br />\n除非你係警察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"敢post唔敢keep，唔可以畀哩類機構再存在"}]}